mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66edb7113070aa8fc7133f04f436ce0b513120f6","tid":2429553,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T19:11:26.000Z","msg":"FIVEM<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c7536396f8d31243dda62f2b319120731c25c69","tid":2429553,"uid":39992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e4d8ca9aedb11ac0841c1796fd886d6a9988f682","tid":2429553,"uid":153496,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5796d9d625f94f473cf1f34148592d62b52bd562","tid":2429553,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b4779f187edc0cf72d2326847b85857ac2967ba","tid":2429553,"uid":153496,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:12:59.000Z","msg":"其實而家呢個時勢先適合出呢啲四圍行下街嘅電腦web game，一收工可以登入四周鳩揈買下衫行下街逃避下現實放鬆下，畀自己精神上都享受下休閒生活，又可以喺隻game入面同人專心吹水鳩噏，唔使逼自己又要刷lv刷裝又剩，打機仲慘過返工。<br />\n手機出呢啲game又係戇鳩，豆潤咁細個mon點會投入到，仲要手機本身就係一種限制，對開發遊戲根本冇好處，好似Yoho夢境排隊唱K咁，用手機根本冇可能做得到咁享受嘅遊戲體驗。<br />\n相反如果你話line play呢啲手機休閒game出電腦版就可以正好多，遊戲開發完全唔需要考慮隻game點樣fit in落電話到。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:51:28.000Z","msg":"依家全部玩跨平台嫁啦...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tKLnvtSwcng\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtKLnvtSwcng&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=63d05a6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tKLnvtSwcng</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zqtcTlTH44o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzqtcTlTH44o&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=d8828fc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zqtcTlTH44o</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_APnuiDRbKI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_APnuiDRbKI&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=9dbc09cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_APnuiDRbKI</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Vv99T4x3l88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVv99T4x3l88&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=30af99b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Vv99T4x3l88</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0871cUc3qok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0871cUc3qok&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=9392baaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0871cUc3qok</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:35:28.000Z","msg":"啱啱諗到一個好重要嘅元素，係隻game要好容許到玩家「掛機」而玩家可以同時投入到隻game。<br />\n譬如你玩啲打怪game掛機打怪完全戇撚鳩，同成個遊戲原意完全相違背，就算你話有啲打怪game可以畀玩家釣下魚遊船河掛機，都只不過係個玩家暫時停落嚟唔打怪，遊戲主軸都係要去打怪，投入隻game就等於唔能夠放鬆，玩呢啲game絕大部份時間都要求玩家全神投入操作。<br />\n又例如有啲巴打提minecraft咁，冇錯，個遊戲嘅性質都係休閒作樂，但個休閒嘅前題都係要個玩家投入操作，每一個動作、行嘅每一步都要控制，所以minecraft都係一隻要有心機先玩到落手嘅game，收工返歸心力交瘁仲邊有心機同你玩minecraft。<br />\n但好似Yoho夢境咁，你唔使好專注，或者可以講係半掛機嘅情況，你就可以輕輕鬆鬆咁投入落隻game到放鬆，享受隻game畀自己嘅回饋。屎忽痕嘅可以撳幾下滑鼠買下家俬裝修下自己屋企，一係就鳩撳幾下行下街買衫，行行下又可以停喺小巨蛋紅館聽人唱歌恥笑人，又可以企定定喺到同game入面萍水相逢嘅新相識鳩噏下，完完全全冇壓力地享受成個遊戲，呢啲先係真真正正嘅休閒。<br />\n就算你講而家出嗰啲VRchat，又係全部遊玩時間都要你全神投入嘅，點容許你鳩揈揈咁放鬆地玩。<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母個臭閪武漢肺炎，如果呢個時候仲有Yoho夢境嘅話簡直完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啱啱睇sooff個網典發現sooff本身都係forum開始，之後再搞個虛擬社區出嚟，連登有冇可能出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T23:32:13.000Z","msg":"上面有巴打提過嘅Tower unite都算滿足到你要求<br />\n隻Game唔會要求你做咩,操作亦唔複雜,得閒就去nightclub跳下舞掛機聽人點嘅歌或者去戲院播下片,有fd陪又可以book間k房,想靜下可以去釣魚,想搵啲野玩可以碌拎,篤波,賭場老虎機,冒險樂園,minigames,你鐘意吹水都可以淨企係廣場同人吹水,非常自由,好適合拎嚟放鬆<br />\n<br />\n雖然隻game冇衫買但都好多傢俬買可以同朋友一齊裝修屋企,起野自由度都好高<br />\n每到大時大節都有啲活動俾玩家玩例如萬聖節有迷宮/尋寶都叫有啲過節氣氛<br />\n隻game會一直更新,間唔中會有返啲新鮮感<br />\n<br />\n缺點就係亞洲ser平時比較少人到weekend 夜晚先多啲人,US ser就通常都會多人<br />\n<br />\n呢隻game有返細個去公園玩嘅感覺,同班陌生人一齊玩,玩完講bye bye 第二日又撞到又一齊玩,熟咗之後請佢去自己屋企玩/去佢屋企玩"},{"pid":"587c379adfcda74380495f1bf0d9979f388e70e5","tid":2429553,"uid":393328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T23:42:40.000Z","msg":"runescape....樓主果陣仲係精蟲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然而家仲有 ser 玩但已經少左好多人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家改成點已經唔知道了"},{"pid":"b16f4ffce8bafec7fe9c1eb3cde97e480d6196fa","tid":2429553,"uid":96704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d97fa05e814494af17a895f86e9b482925b51f9","tid":2429553,"uid":153496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8d77d637a4645bc5ddd8a215ad7b2437c5cb34a6","tid":2429553,"uid":109923,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:29:53.000Z","msg":"SOOFF"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:36:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_XStaS8fvHg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_XStaS8fvHg&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=7129535e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_XStaS8fvHg</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T23:43:36.000Z","msg":"細個中學個陣一放學就狗衝返屋企玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我記得前排好似係隻驚既其中一個GM話搞緊再開返個ser？"},{"pid":"3e0c275e2bd3c615f9cd906551ce16a69a783dbe","tid":2429553,"uid":542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"reply